n like this."],[6377,6502,"How’d it happen?"],[6577,6752,"I was five,"],[6840,7073,"and my cousin Zoe, she..."],[7399,7528,"I got your doll."],[7565,7695,"Changed my mind."],[7707,7841,"I don't want the doll any more."],[7874,7945,"And I don't want you"],[7945,8049,"in my house either."],[8525,8929,"And my aunt said that I just fell"],[8929,9180,"and was clumsy, and they never"],[9180,9330,"took me to the hospital."],[9522,9743,"They're not going to get away with this."],[9755,9884,"I promise you that."],[10022,10151,"Okay?"],[11232,11457,"The hottest hockey player’s fiancée..."],[11457,11619,"is Cripplerella?"],[11857,12116,"I will never allow my son"],[12132,12328,"to marry that gold digger."]],"44":[[91,254,"That's kind of weird..."],[258,400,"That's not even funny."],[437,567,"No, it's not..."],[771,859,"Mom!"],[971,1055,"I'm glad you're here,"],[1059,1209,"this is Lila."],[1572,1710,"I try not to interfere,"],[1755,1918,"but who is this girl?"],[1960,2089,"Your fiancée?"],[2089,2214,"Really?"],[2214,2344,"Mom, that's enough."],[2548,2727,"You don't have to marry her."],[2727,2877,"I want to marry her, mom."],[2936,3065,"And more importantly,"],[3123,3257,"we share a son."],[3457,3561,"You're a grandmother now."],[3561,3695,"You should be happy."],[3870,4079,"Did he just say he wants to marry me?"],[4212,4341,"I have a grandson?"],[4729,4859,"Oh, Lila."],[4875,4979,"I'm sorry."],[4979,5109,"I shouldn't have interfered."],[5113,5238,"I was just so worried"],[5238,5401,"that Alex was being tricked."],[5447,5534,"No. It's okay."],[5534,5764,"You just care about your son."],[5843,5976,"Like I do."],[6001,6147,"I'm glad that we have that"],[6147,6235,"in common."],[6289,6594,"Can I meet my grandson, please?"],[6619,6723,"Yeah. Of course."],[6723,6894,"He's just sleeping upstairs and..."]],"45":[[16,145,"He's perfect."],[187,487,"The cutest baby in the whole world."],[621,813,"I'd like to stay a few days"],[846,1067,"so I can spoil him properly."],[1276,1459,"Have you